WEBVTT

00:00.932 --> 00:05.635
It is a time of innovation and progress, when the world's greatest minds...

00:05.836 --> 00:07.585
...pushed the limits of what's possible...

00:10.264 --> 00:12.709
...and delved deep into the unthinkable.

00:15.607 --> 00:18.673
My friend, Victor Frankenstein, is one such man.

00:20.185 --> 00:22.961
I dream of a world where hope replaces faith,...

00:23.835 --> 00:27.594
...where a crippled man can be healed to walk again.

00:27.907 --> 00:31.858
What if we could give every life the chance it deserved?

00:32.481 --> 00:35.293
Igor, help me change the world.

